{
  "lines": [
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "失落圣殿... 圣剑骑士团的圣地。",
      "expression": "normal"
    },
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "圣殿骑士长「金卫」... 曾是我最敬重的导师。",
      "expression": "normal"
    },
    {
      "character": "Goldguard",
      "text": "我的学生... 你终究还是来了。",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Goldguard",
      "text": "我守在这里，不让任何人接近圣物核心。",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Goldguard",
      "text": "圣物已被污染。碎片只会传播腐化。",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "导师... 为什么？",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Goldguard",
      "text": "我让你离开，是想让你活下去。",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Goldguard",
      "text": "但你选择了执念。来吧，用剑证明你的选择。",
      "expression": "determined"
    }
  ]
}